"{\"uid\": \"jamaicaobserver.com-2024-08-04-lyn-pays-tribute-idol-alia-atkinson-olympic-debut\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"PARIS, France - Fast-rising Jamaican swimmer Sabrina Lyn failed to qualify from the heats of the 50m freestyle at La Defense Arena yesterday but left determined to continue her quest to emulate her heroine and inspiration Alia Atkinson.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 236, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 28, \"end\": 36, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"score\": 0.9994253118466137, \"rank\": 0.0005748115218540082, \"text\": \"Jamaican\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\"}, {\"begin\": 222, \"end\": 235, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alia_Atkinson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Alia Atkinson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alia_Atkinson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alia_Atkinson\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"PARIS\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 5}, {\"ngram\": \"the heats\", \"from\": 80, \"to\": 89}, {\"ngram\": \"the 50m freestyle\", \"from\": 93, \"to\": 110}, {\"ngram\": \"La Defense Arena\", \"from\": 114, \"to\": 130}, {\"ngram\": \"her quest\", \"from\": 173, \"to\": 182}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Lyn registered a time of 26.08 seconds to finish fifth in her heat, 29th overall out of the 79 starters.\", \"from\": 238, \"to\": 342, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Lyn\", \"from\": 238, \"to\": 241}, {\"ngram\": \"a time\", \"from\": 253, \"to\": 259}, {\"ngram\": \"26.08 seconds\", \"from\": 263, \"to\": 276}, {\"ngram\": \"her heat\", \"from\": 296, \"to\": 304}, {\"ngram\": \"the 79 starters\", \"from\": 326, \"to\": 341}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was below her best-ever time of 25.82, set at the Carifta Games in The Bahamas last April, and she reflected on a slower-than-desired start in a frenetic event during which there is no room for hesitation of any kind.\", \"from\": 344, \"to\": 564, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 414, \"end\": 425, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Bahamas\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.398691286163986e-18, \"text\": \"The Bahamas\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Bahamas\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Bahamas\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her best-ever time\", \"from\": 357, \"to\": 375}, {\"ngram\": \"the Carifta Games\", \"from\": 393, \"to\": 410}, {\"ngram\": \"a slower-than-desired start\", \"from\": 459, \"to\": 486}, {\"ngram\": \"a frenetic event\", \"from\": 490, \"to\": 506}, {\"ngram\": \"no room\", \"from\": 529, \"to\": 536}, {\"ngram\": \"hesitation\", \"from\": 541, \"to\": 551}, {\"ngram\": \"any kind\", \"from\": 555, \"to\": 563}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Drawn in lane six, she was always playing catch-up and completed the single length behind winner Jenjira Srisa-ard, from Thailand, and three others.\", \"from\": 566, \"to\": 714, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 687, \"end\": 695, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thailand\", \"score\": 0.8664844992932347, \"rank\": 0.14161826023365173, \"text\": \"Thailand\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thailand\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thailand\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"lane\", \"from\": 575, \"to\": 579}, {\"ngram\": \"catch-up\", \"from\": 608, \"to\": 616}, {\"ngram\": \"the single length\", \"from\": 631, \"to\": 648}, {\"ngram\": \"winner Jenjira Srisa-ard\", \"from\": 656, \"to\": 680}, {\"ngram\": \"three others\", \"from\": 701, \"to\": 713}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 20-year-old, Kingston-born student was performing in front of an almost-capacity 15,000 audience at the vast, multipurpose venue - home to French Rugby Union giants Racing 69 and where the likes of pop superstars the Rolling Stones, Bruce Springsteen, and Paul McCartney have played.\", \"from\": 716, \"to\": 1003, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 859, \"end\": 865, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\", \"score\": 0.6078247485994567, \"rank\": 0.6079967375638936, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\"}, {\"begin\": 872, \"end\": 877, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999999062106371, \"rank\": 9.255112612010227e-08, \"text\": \"Union\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 937, \"end\": 951, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rolling_Stone\", \"score\": 0.7572754998942368, \"rank\": 0.32052337641927275, \"text\": \"Rolling Stones\", \"types\": [\"Q41298\", \"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rolling_Stone\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rolling_Stone\"}, {\"begin\": 953, \"end\": 970, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bruce_Springsteen\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Bruce Springsteen\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bruce_Springsteen\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bruce_Springsteen\"}, {\"begin\": 976, \"end\": 990, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paul_McCartney\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.4825836214709694e-14, \"text\": \"Paul McCartney\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paul_McCartney\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paul_McCartney\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Kingston-born student\", \"from\": 733, \"to\": 754}, {\"ngram\": \"front\", \"from\": 773, \"to\": 778}, {\"ngram\": \"an almost-capacity 15,000 audience\", \"from\": 782, \"to\": 816}, {\"ngram\": \"the vast, multipurpo